{"tid":1534242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠錄音","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:08:54.000Z","uid":201438,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9df559c98691602f0d06edd99ed3cebad8071f","tid":1534242,"uid":201438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:53:26.000Z","msg":"不必理會，完。"},{"pid":"6763150f9b0fb2c370f87f3d11f6da247e79a600","tid":1534242,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:53:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f868dd0bb18443efb604068faac4c861cf59dde","tid":1534242,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:54:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=0e8c265f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 908都要照上街<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"eb40afd2effa4e6502e42047de3d8791dc795e9a","tid":1534242,"uid":201438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"